text: Bethesda has wares.. if you have the coin.

A very nice artwork piece. One of the members of the battle of Mogadishu, Randall Shughart, a Delta sniper, went to my school in 1993. West Perry Senior high. 

I didn't intend to make this conversation weird, I just wanted to share a little tidbit. Anyways, that's the connection I have with this artwork. But very well done!
